{
  "doc_id": "31866",
  "text": "The strains BJ3505 Suc2 and BJ3505 were transformed with plasmids YEpFLAG-1, YEpMEL1, and YEpMEL1His, by a modification of the lithium acetate method [CITATION_1] . Transformants were selected on solid CM-Trp after 48 h at 30 • C. A single colony was taken to prepare a liquid CM-Trp pre-culture up to an optical density at 600 nm (OD 600 ) of 5 (stationary phase) at 30 • C and 250 rpm for 72 h, which was used to inoculate up to units OD 600 corresponding to each production culture tested, as described above.",
